iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/k80J5WLgt0pziKjPJ7fLTp9cQwg.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/drSMt5W8SxnmOcRL5dMEe650kyy.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/uK0w0NB4FwpUgEvP6VSDWMkhdZo.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1600,"height":900,"file_path":"/3hiBoYhvB6IXPOuT0EoZcMynMH3.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1600,"height":900,"file_path":"/cqmNKSoyPbtr9u3F8EIRy3e48mX.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1600,"height":900,"file_path":"/fkHQmkwBriA3mlOOY7VHg4NG7j9.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":721,"file_path":"/9GbNK2WGnuVGRPQ2oXT6UghM4aT.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.775,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/aBGXu5fjwwc8DWylgyL7AlKcGG2.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1842,"height":1036,"file_path":"/xHeHvnq22bTVrObH9ue7KOsucXK.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1442,"height":811,"file_path":"/rUDqlINd9SerpaK06HOKV3ZXyhk.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1284,"height":720,"file_path":"/jdZ021BOtYdD0yg5Y2fqmUagVTb.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.783,"vote_average":0},{"width":1356,"height":763,"file_path":"/uNJvAxu4QvPjAvISwFzuyWrNEg1.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":1376,"height":773,"file_path":"/mwBG9LJpnZgUasxvUCeYfGoOdWj.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.78,"vote_average":0},{"width":1283,"height":721,"file_path":"/3HaHGUZ9t0CJ0puF13xBK7gk0BD.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.779,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/fa641zFp4XlesOdGDJrP7wQhq6l.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/mbcbterBAThwYEcNToZ2WCvqGK.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/6CEimiL6eAoazc0ei7GP07QnBB5.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T07:47:36.945+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Salò, or the 120 Days of Sodom","runtime":117,"tagline":"The final vision of a controversial filmmaker.","homepage":"","overview":"Four corrupted fascist libertines round up 9 teenage boys and girls and subject them to 120 days of sadistic physical, mental and sexual torture."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Die 120 Tage von Sodom","runtime":116,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"In der Republik von „Salò“, dem letzten Refugium italienischer Faschisten kurz vor dem Ende der Mussolini-Herrschaft, inszeniert eine Gruppe sadistischer Großbürger terroristische Grausamkeitsrituale: Junge Männer und Frauen werden als Lust- und Folterobjekt missbraucht und erniedrigt, schließlich in einer perversen Orgie zu Tode gequält. – Pier Paolo Pasolinis Abrechnung mit dem Faschismus."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Salò o le 120 giornate di Sodoma","runtime":116,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Durante la Repubblica di Salò quattro signori, che rappresentano i quattro poteri, si riuniscono insieme a quattro Megere, ex meretrici, e a una schiera di ragazzi e ragazze, partigiani o figli di partigiani in una villa isolata e protetta dai soldati repubblichini e dalle SS. Per 120 giorni sarà in vigore un regolamento che permette ai Signori di disporre a piacere delle loro vittime."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Salo, avagy Sodoma 120 napja","runtime":116,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Az utolsó Pasolini-film De Sade márki nyomán: négy fasiszta egy villában a legváltozatosabb szexuális kínzásoknak veti alá a foglyokat. \"A Saloval mindazokhoz fordulok, akik hozzám hasonlóan gyűlölik a Hatalmat, azért, amit az emberi testtel művel: dologgá aljasítja, s ezáltal az embert megfosztja a személyiségétől... Én különös hévvel gyűlölöm azt a hatalmat, amelytől most, 1975-ben szenvedek. Ez a hatalom olyan rettenetes eszközökkel manipulálja a testet, hogy még Hitlertől sincs mit irigyelnie: ...új, elidegenített és hazug értékrendet hirdet, a fogyasztó társadalom értékeit. Ma az megy végbe éppen, amit Marx az élő, valódi, korábbi kultúrák megsemmisítésének nevezett...\" (Pasolini)"},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Salò, eller Sodoms 120 dagar","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ett antal högt uppsatta fascister kidnappar några ungdomar och för dem till en avlägsen plats för att sedan förnedra, våldta och tortera dem. Berättelsen bygger på romanen \"Les 120 journées de Sodome, ou l'École du libertinage\" av markis de Sade från år 1785, men handlingen är förlagd till den s.k. Salòrepubliken, det av Nazityskland ockuperade Norditalien 1944–45."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Salò ou les 120 Journées de Sodome","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Durant la République fasciste de Salò, quatre seigneurs élaborent un règlement pervers auquel ils vont se conformer. Ils sélectionnent huit représentants des deux sexes qui deviendront les victimes de leurs pratiques les plus dégradantes. Tous s'enferment alors dans une villa près de Marzabotto afin d'y passer 120 journées en respectant les règles de leur code terrifiant."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Saló, o los 120 días de Sodoma","runtime":116,"tagline":"La visión final de un cineasta controvertido.","homepage":"","overview":"En una mansión, cuatro señores se reúnen con cuatro exprostitutas y con un grupo de jóvenes de ambos sexos, partisanos o hijos de partisanos, que han sido hechos prisioneros. Nadie en la casa puede eludir las reglas del juego establecidas por los señores; toda transgresión se castiga con la muerte. Además, ellos gozan de la facultad de disponer a su antojo de la vida de los cautivos."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Salò aneb 120 dnů sodomy","runtime":117,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Fašistická Itálie. Čtveřice vysoce postavených mužů si přiveze do paláce skupinu chlapců a dívek, kteří jim po následujících několik měsíců budou pod taktovkou čtyř prostitutek sloužit jako prostředníci k naplnění všech rozkoší – včetně těch nejzvrácenějších! Absolutní moc, kterou nad svými obětmi mají, je vede až k samé hranici únosnosti, za níž už se ztrácí veškerá lidskost a zbývá jen syrová brutalita a perverze."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"索多玛120天","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"《索多玛的120天》取材于18世纪法国作家萨德的小说，而帕索里尼将时空转换到二次大战末期的意大利，影片所表现的背景是墨索里尼体制的最臭名昭著的一段史实——“萨罗共和国”是第二次世界大战最后18个月中法西主义的最后堡垒，在这段统治期间，有72000人惨遭屠杀，40000人被截肢，大量的人被送入集中营，一大批妇女，少年被奸污或鸡奸。萨罗是意大利人极力想忘却的一段历史。但帕索里尼在灵感的触发下，把这一历史暴行的内容和事实与萨德的小说的大量色情内容结合起来。帕索里尼改编了原著中最不堪入目的部分，随着时间、地点改变，而使他的影片带有明显的政治色彩。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Saló ou os 120 Dias de Sodoma","runtime":116,"tagline":"A visão final de um cineasta controverso.","homepage":"","overview":"No norte de Itália em 1944, a República de Saló permanecia sob o controlo nazi. Quatro homens de poder, posição e prestígio, reúnem à força 16 jovens belos e perfeitos de ambos os sexos, que levam com criados e guardas armados para um palácio perto de Marzabotto. Aí três senhoras de meia idade contam bizarras histórias que os senhores recriam ou parodiam no palácio servindo-se dos jovens de forma arbitrária. Passam assim pelos ciclos das Manias, da Merda e do Sangue, num crescendo de deboche, delírio sexual, humilhações, torturas e finalmente morte."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Salo, czyli 120 dni Sodomy","runtime":117,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Akcja filmu rozgrywa się we Włoszech na przełomie 1944-45. W willi mieszka czterech szlachetnie urodzonych panów: sędzia, biskup, książe i bankier, a ich towarzyszkami są cztery rozwiązłe kobiety.  Ludzie ci dobierają sobie ofiary do orgii, wśród miejscowej ludności.  Porywają ośmioro młodych chłopców i dziewcząt. Dla młodych, niewinnych ludzi zaczynają się dni przepełnione seksualnym poniżaniem, perwersją i sadyzmem."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":116,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Italië tijdens de Tweede Wereldoorlog. Plaats van handeling: een afgelegen landhuis aan het Gardameer. Een hertog, een bankier, een politicus en een geestelijke laten negen jongens en negen meisjes bijeenbrengen. Terwijl drie courtisanes scabreuze verhalen vertellen ter inspiratie, vergrijpen de mannen zich op allerlei manieren aan de gevangenen. Een scala van sadistische en scatologische perversiteiten passeert de revue, uitmondend in een gruwelijke moordpartij waarbij de achttien jongens en meisjes worden doodgemarteld, terwijl de mannen om beurten met een verrekijker toekijken."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Σαλό ή 120 Μέρες στα Σόδομα","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Το 1944, στο Σαλό της βόρειας Ιταλίας, τέσσερις φασίστες που εκπροσωπούν τις βασικές μορφές εξουσίας κλείνουν διά της βίας σε απομονωμένο παλάτι μια ομάδα παρθένων αγοριών και κοριτσιών. Τρεις πόρνες αφηγούνται τις εμπειρίες τους, ενώ οι ενήλικες εξαναγκάζουν τους κρατούμενους να συμμετάσχουν σε πράξεις ακραίου και σαδομαζοχιστικού σεξ.\r Το \"Σαλό\", μια ταινία που αρνείται να μπει στη διαδικασία του να προσπαθήσει να γίνει αρεστή σε οποιοδήποτε είδος κοινού, ήταν η ύστατη ταινία που γύρισε ο Pasolini. Λίγους μήνες αργότερα, η βία, ένα από τα θέματα που ανέλυσε διεξοδικά μέσα από το έργο του, σφράγισε οριστικά και την ίδια του τη ζωή."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Сало, или 120 дней Содома","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Экранизируя роман маркиза де Сада, Пазолини переносит действие в 1944-45-е годы, в фашистскую «республику Сало» на севере Италии, где группа лиц из высшего общества во главе с принцем унижает, издевается, мучает, пытает юношей и девушек, собранных для услаждения извращённой элиты, чувствующей свою погибель. Четыре месяца длится эта экзекуция. Для взрослых это последняя возможность удовлетворить свои низменные инстинкты, для молодых людей — расплата за свою юность и желание жить."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Сало, або 120 днів Содому","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Дуже вільна інтерпретація скандально відомої фантазії де Сада \"120 днів Содому\" переносить глядача в 1944 рік, в республіку Сало на півночі Італії, в останні дні італійського фашизму. Магістрат, банкір, герцог і монсеньйор заманюють групу молодих чоловіків і жінок на ізольовану віллу, де їх піддають безжальним, майже ритуальним тортурам, посвячують полонених в правила гри, побудованої на сексуальних збоченнях. \"Вперше я знімаю фільм про сучасний світ, - говорив режисер - порушуючи всі мислимі умовності буржуазного смаку\". Фільм розділено на три частини відповідно до Пекла за де Садом: коло безумства, коло екскрементів і коло крові. В результаті, не дивлячись на незаперечно геніальні моменти, вийшла стрічка, яку майже нестерпно дивитися."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Salò eller de 120 dage i Sodoma","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Pasolinis sidste film er dette voldsomme politiske manifest, der placerer Marquis de Sades roman i Mussolinis fascistiske Italien anno 1944. Pasolini observerer, uden at blinke, en lille sadistisk overklassegruppes systematiske fornedrelse og tortur af en gruppe teenagere. Filmen blev mødt med totalforbud i Italien og står stadig den dag i dag som et af de mest kontroversielle værker i filmhistorien."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"סאלו או 120 הימים של סדום","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"פייר פאולו פזוליני, משורר, סופר ובמאי, מרקסיסט נלהב שנזרק מן המפלגה הקומוניסטית בגלל היותו הומוסקסואל, יצר במהלך הקריירה שלו סרטים שנויים במחלוקות  אך אף אחד מהם אינו מתקרב ל\"סאלו או 120 הימים של סדום\", אותו הספיק לסיים קודם שנרצח.  עיבודו של פזוליני לספרו של המרקיז דה סאד הוא אולי אחד הסרטים המטרידים והדוחים שנעשו אי פעם. הוא גם אחד החשובים שנעשה. הסרט מותח ביקורת חריפה על הפאשיזם והאידאליזם, וטוען שגאולה מוסרית היא רק מיתוס. הבמאי העביר את עלילת הספר לרפובליקה של סאלו, מדינת בובות פשיסטית בחסות נאצית. נשיא, דוכס, בישוף ושופט דקדנטיים שחוטפים קבוצה של גברים ונשים צעירים לווילה מבודדת כדי לענות ולנצל אותם מינית. אונס, רצח, אכילת צואה הם רק השלב הראשון במסכת ההשפלות והברוטאליות. הסרט קשה מאוד לצפייה והוא נאסר לשידור במדינות רבות. בישראל, הצנזורה על סרטים ומחזות מעולם לא התירה את הקרנתו (עד ביטולה של זו ב-1991)."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Salo ya da Sodom'un 120 günü","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mutlak güç, mutlak yozlaşmayı getirir. Topluma önderlik eden dört insan, özel olarak seçilen genç kız ve oğlanları sistematik bir biçimde aşağılayarak onlardan yararlanır ve işkence eder...  Bir dizi müstehcen öyküyle başlayan bu sefahat dolu işkence, dinsel bir tören havasının ardına gizlenmiştir. Filmin gelişimi cinsel sapıklıktan sadizme, işkenceden ölüme kadar amansızca uzanır. İşkencelerin alacağı bir zevk yoktur, acımaları da...  Pasolini'nin son filminde bir ölüm kokusu, çöküş ve umutsuzluk sancıları içinde kıvranan insanlığa soyutlanmış son bir ağıt yatar. Faşizme karşı zehir zemberek bu film, kasvetli bir tür vasiyettir sanki..."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Salò, ou os 120 Dias de Sodoma","runtime":117,"tagline":"A obra final e definitiva de Pier Paolo Pasolini.","homepage":"","overview":"Pasolini parte da obra de Sade e revisita o episódio histórico da República de Salò para apresentar sua visão sobre o poder, a sexualidade, o conformismo e a juventude italiana dos anos 1970, em um filme de quatro partes: Ante-Inferno, Círculo das Manias, Círculo da Merda e uma última, Círculo de Sangue."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Sodoman 120 päivää","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"살로 소돔의 120일","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"제 3 제국의 운명이 끝을 향해가고 있을 무렵, 타락한 이탈리아 귀족들 네 사람이 성욕을 마음껏 분출할 수 있는 천국을 만들기로 합의한다. 악명이 자자한 뚜쟁이 네 사람을 확보한 뒤 나치군인 몇 사람을 끌어 모은다. 이 타락한 귀족들은 이탈리아 10대 소년 소녀 백여 명을 강제로 데려와 \"재미와 게임\"을 위해 외딴 빌라에 가둬 놓는다. 권력자들은 매일 어떤 방식으로 성욕을 분출할지 회의하고 그 수위도 점점 높아지는데…"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Saló o los 120 días de Sodoma","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En una mansión, cuatro señores se reúnen con cuatro exprostitutas y con un grupo de jóvenes de ambos sexos, partisanos o hijos de partisanos, que han sido hechos prisioneros. Nadie en la casa puede eludir las reglas del juego establecidas por los señores; toda transgresión se castiga con la muerte. Además, ellos gozan de la facultad de disponer a su antojo de la vida de los cautivos."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"索多瑪120天","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"四個主掌政治社會體制的權勢人物共謀，逮捕了十八位少男少女，在鄉間城堡內進行匪夷所思的強迫性交與虐殺，好讓主人們興奮起來。帕索裡尼（Pier Paolo Pasolini）將薩德侯爵的名著和當代極權主義掛勾，用露骨的色情想像詮釋極權暴行，一面世即引起廣泛爭議。題材雖如此驚世駭俗，大膽的集體全裸場面，毫不迴避的性倒錯景觀，全片卻畫面對稱、構圖典雅、美術雕琢，甚至結構也井然仿自但丁《神曲》，如一幅無懈可擊的古典派繪畫。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"სალო, ანუ სოდომის 120 დღე","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"4 გარყვნილი ფაშისტი რყვნის 9 თინეიჯერ გოგოსა და ბიჭს და ატყვევებს მათ 120 დღიან სადისტურ ფიზიკურ, მენტალურ და სექსუალურ ტყვეობაში"},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"ソドムの市","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1944年、第2次大戦下の北イタリア。ナチズムに加担する公爵、大司教、最高判事、大統領の4人の権力者は町中から美少年美少女達を狩り集め、レイプ・スカトロ・ホモ・ソドミー・オナニー・そして虐殺と、ありとあらゆる想像を絶した地獄のパノラマを繰り広げる。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"สุขนาฏกรรมอเวจี","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"กลุ่มฟาสซิสต์เสรีนิยมทุจริต 4 คนจับกลุ่มเด็กชายและเด็กหญิงวัยรุ่น 9 คน และทรมานพวกเขาด้วยวิธีการทรมานร่างกาย จิตใจ และทางเพศอย่างโหดร้ายเป็นเวลา 120 วัน"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Salò sau cele 120 de zile de sodomie","runtime":0,"tagline":"Versiunea finală a unui făcător de filme controversat.","homepage":"","overview":"Patru libertini fasciști corupți adună 9 adolescenți și adolescente și îi supun la 120 de zile de tortură sadică fizică, psihică și sexuală."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"سالو یا ۱۲۰ روز در سدوم","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"در جنگ جهانی دوم در ایتالیا، چهار آزادیخواه فاشیست ۹ پسر و دختر نوجوان را جمع کردند و ۱۲۰ روز تحت شکنجه جسمی، روحی و جنسی قرار دادند."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Saló ehk Soodoma 120 päeva","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"},{"data":{"title":"索多瑪 120 天","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"四個主掌政治社會體制的權勢人物共謀，逮捕了十八位少男少女，在鄉間城堡內進行匪夷所思的強迫性交與虐殺，好讓主人們興奮起來。帕索裏尼（Pier Paolo Pasolini）將薩德侯爵的名著和當代極權主義掛勾，用露骨的色情想像詮釋極權暴行，一面世即引起廣泛爭議。題材雖如此驚世駭俗，大膽的集體全裸場面，毫不迴避的性倒錯景觀，全片卻畫面對稱、構圖典雅、美術雕琢，甚至結構也井然仿自但丁《神曲》，如一幅無懈可擊的古典派繪畫。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Salo jeb 120 Sodomas dienas","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"630d057618864b0080e55b8f","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/630d057618864b0080e55b8f","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$11","created_at":"2022-08-29T18:29:10.326Z","updated_at":"2022-08-29T18:29:10.407Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":5,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}},{"id":"647fa17671ffdf012d67cbaa","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/647fa17671ffdf012d67cbaa","author":"DougG_YVR","content":"Wow! You can't escape the fact that this movie pushes the limits of disturbing art! Many will call it sick. I suspect the point of this film is more about the depravity and dehumanization of fascism, political corruption, totalitarianism, and morality. I have not read the Marquis de Sade's work on which this film was based.\r\n\r\n**It isn't possible to \"un-see\" a film, so be prepared if you choose the experience.** It was described to me as \"horror\" before I watched it, and I'm not sure it truly captures the film's genre. I can't think of a film genre that adequately describes it.\r\n\r\nI will probably never watch it again or forget the images it seared on my brain. But I was challenged to think about various political and societal themes that are still very relevant today.","created_at":"2023-06-06T21:13:26.952Z","updated_at":"2023-06-07T14:22:09.359Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":7,"username":"DougG_YVR","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":12491,"adult":false,"title":"Accattone","video":false,"overview":"A pimp with no other means to provide for himself finds his life spiralling out of control when his prostitute is sent to prison.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0021,"vote_count":511,"poster_path":"/113ts2Bmm5CZ3YJMwfCU9XGFCAf.jpg","release_date":"1961-09-25","vote_average":7.708,"backdrop_path":"/rJSCS5EP9JGjNECa5hEB9Bsibjf.jpg","original_title":"Accattone","original_language":"it"},{"id":485835,"adult":false,"title":"12","video":false,"overview":"Anton and Erika started out as friends for five years and got into a romantic relationship for seven years. Anton is a commercial director while Erika is a former band member and becomes his stay-at-home partner. The day finally comes when he asks her to marry him.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3597,"vote_count":47,"poster_path":"/2soiPmVw9khjoxPe5Jt8M12oZQL.jpg","release_date":"2017-11-08","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/eEr2INOXP0IjsxN4MixZ0twFKcb.jpg","original_title":"12","original_language":"tl"},{"id":5335,"adult":false,"title":"Theorem","video":false,"overview":"A wealthy Italian household is turned upside down when a handsome stranger arrives, seduces every family member and then disappears. Each has an epiphany of sorts, but none can figure out who the seductive visitor was or why he came.","genre_ids":[9648,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4692,"vote_count":438,"poster_path":"/k7rEBaYUTgdxVqYl9aZm5ZcoB41.jpg","release_date":"1968-09-07","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/7o5uc27hJD4L95ZnJO9CR5iHdfQ.jpg","original_title":"Teorema","original_language":"it"},{"id":8689,"adult":false,"title":"Cannibal Holocaust","video":false,"overview":"A New York University professor returns from a rescue mission to the Amazon rainforest with the footage shot by a lost team of documentarians who were making a film about the area's local cannibal tribes.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.9907,"vote_count":1814,"poster_path":"/otxZzMh53TsN7yYFqSZ3rwH1yMd.jpg","release_date":"1980-02-07","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/7QBBvE6tA1kUlo7AKeZZMygdSHp.jpg","original_title":"Cannibal Holocaust","original_language":"it"},{"id":542507,"adult":false,"title":"Princess Principal Crown Handler: Chapter 1","video":false,"overview":"The story is set in London at the end of the 19th century. A new task has been assigned to Team White Pigeon, a group of spies from the Commonwealth. It is a delivery of a used bookstore owner to the Commonwealth. Ange, Dorothy and Chise successfully recapture the owner, who had been held in a detention center by the Kingdom. Meanwhile, the \"spy hunt\" became more intense in the Kingdom following an assassination attempt on the queen, and tension is strained at Control in the Commonwealth. Control speculates that the spy who has dispatched to the royal family might be a \"double agent.\" To find out the truth, they order Team White Pigeon to contact with the spy, whose codename is \"Bishop.\" How their new mission will be accomplished? And who is \"Bishop\"?","genre_ids":[16,28,12,18,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.802,"vote_count":45,"poster_path":"/iD09UJgG3SIfmI28YsfzYwB6AZQ.jpg","release_date":"2021-02-11","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/x6moftKN2ZniaukHJwJDXzaxiPu.jpg","original_title":"プリンセス・プリンシパル Crown Handler 第1章","original_language":"ja"},{"id":73861,"adult":false,"title":"A Serbian Film","video":false,"overview":"Retired porn star Milos leads a normal family life trying to make ends meet. Presented with the opportunity of a lifetime to financially support his family for the rest of their lives, Milos must participate in one last mysterious film. From then on, Milos is drawn into a maelstrom of unbelievable cruelty and mayhem.","genre_ids":[80,27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.9348,"vote_count":2176,"poster_path":"/cToUzXZ9AcUylfIt8vnXhiy6Y9m.jpg","release_date":"2010-01-06","vote_average":5.431,"backdrop_path":"/o0x4LOW8qzVNyqwWGMuFa3kE7Hs.jpg","original_title":"Srpski film","original_language":"sr"},{"id":33583,"adult":false,"title":"The Decameron","video":false,"overview":"A young Sicilian is swindled twice, but ends up rich; a man poses as a deaf-mute in a convent of curious nuns; a woman must hide her lover when her husband comes home early; a scoundrel fools a priest on his deathbed; three brothers take revenge on their sister's lover; a young girl sleeps on the roof to meet her boyfriend at night; a group of painters wait for inspiration; a crafty priest attempts to seduce his friend's wife; and two friends make a pact to find out what happens after death.","genre_ids":[36,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.2858,"vote_count":351,"poster_path":"/iL5mmuIL6fqFSWJeHE417WWrocz.jpg","release_date":"1971-08-25","vote_average":6.818,"backdrop_path":"/9CbH2EktREWAur7XLBeFNFNr5BQ.jpg","original_title":"Il Decameron","original_language":"it"},{"id":13002,"adult":false,"title":"Barbie in the 12 Dancing Princesses","video":false,"overview":"King Randolph sends for his cousin, Duchess Rowena, to help turn his daughters, Princess Genevieve and her eleven sisters, into royal material. But the Duchess strips the sisters of their fun, including their favorite pastime: dancing. When all hope may be lost, the sisters discover a secret passageway to a magical land where they can dance the night away.","genre_ids":[16,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.8375,"vote_count":1232,"poster_path":"/yBB7PwXRFJ29U8m8SnTcWVizFvM.jpg","release_date":"2006-09-19","vote_average":7.604,"backdrop_path":"/1KzmjDbhHwBARDzzZZKNC3tqqgd.jpg","original_title":"Barbie in the 12 Dancing Princesses","original_language":"en"},{"id":47796,"adult":false,"title":"Mamma Roma","video":false,"overview":"After years spent working as a prostitute in her Italian village, middle-aged Mamma Roma has saved enough money to buy herself a fruit stand so that she can have a respectable middle-class life and reestablish contact with the 16-year-old son she abandoned when he was an infant. But her former pimp threatens to expose her sordid past, and her troubled son seems destined to fall into a life of crime and violence.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6622,"vote_count":434,"poster_path":"/aMPxSiapchjZb73Lz7yNMdTi1cc.jpg","release_date":"1962-09-22","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/4OqoSolfhNesDAfv2zluIDVXiPR.jpg","original_title":"Mamma Roma","original_language":"it"},{"id":24192,"adult":false,"title":"The Gospel According to St. Matthew","video":false,"overview":"Along a rocky, barren coastline, Jesus begins teaching, primarily using parables. He attracts disciples; he's stern, brusque, and demanding. His parables often take on the powers that be, so he and his teachings come to the attention of the Pharisees, the chief priests, and elders. They conspire to have him arrested, beaten, tried, and crucified, just as he prophesied to his followers.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7318,"vote_count":401,"poster_path":"/oifi2CQkKbb6Y2x6J5K6CjaKab9.jpg","release_date":"1965-03-03","vote_average":7.439,"backdrop_path":"/iz7xP1INmMTAfRKaToWVmXrrE1P.jpg","original_title":"Il vangelo secondo Matteo","original_language":"it"},{"id":47406,"adult":false,"title":"Arabian Nights","video":false,"overview":"The final part of Pasolini's Trilogy of Life series is rich with exotic tales of slaves and kings, potions, betrayals, demons and, most of all, love and lovemaking in all its myriad forms. Mysterious and liberating, this is an exquisitely dreamlike and adult interpretation of the original folk tales.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2051,"vote_count":222,"poster_path":"/zDrAREfrNvq5O10lHDDh529i143.jpg","release_date":"1974-06-20","vote_average":6.462,"backdrop_path":"/fp315t2MuJs3jOPPsoY2Jv7ZdPQ.jpg","original_title":"Il fiore delle Mille e una notte","original_language":"it"},{"id":48688,"adult":false,"title":"Pigsty","video":false,"overview":"Two dramatic stories. In an undetermined past, a young cannibal (who killed his own father) is condemned to be torn to pieces by some wild beasts. In the second story, Julian, the young son of a post-war German industrialist, is on the way to lie down with his farm's pigs, because he doesn't like human relationships.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7429,"vote_count":161,"poster_path":"/9FZmcZ9EH4sk9WxLe90m0ddRpnC.jpg","release_date":"1969-09-02","vote_average":7.028,"backdrop_path":"/y5iVIhe8WcGlOOSQu2K72wX7nvl.jpg","original_title":"Porcile","original_language":"it"},{"id":57084,"adult":false,"title":"Satanic Pandemonium","video":false,"overview":"Sister Maria is known in the convent for her good works and charity, but, in the secret depths of her sexual fantasies, she is tormented by visions of another world - a world where her forbidden passions are allowed to run free. In this world Satan is her master. As her acts of violence and blasphemy mount, Maria realizes that she has been chosen by the Devil to destroy the convent and lead her sister nuns into hell!","genre_ids":[27,9648,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5136,"vote_count":94,"poster_path":"/k6LZn3greNmaYhySVnwUkkDmlpo.jpg","release_date":"1975-06-26","vote_average":6.399,"backdrop_path":"/fQ9CL9i2dHYG5poGHv1WEubo9XL.jpg","original_title":"Satánico pandemonium: la sexorcista","original_language":"es"},{"id":523707,"adult":false,"title":"Nastya and Egor","video":false,"overview":"The main characters of the film are members of the group \"Nastya\" Nastya Poleva and Yegor Belkin. The half-hour half-documentary tape included footage taken by Balabanov in 1985-1990. In addition to the main characters, the documentary footage captured many prominent figures of Sverdlovsk rock club, in particular Vyacheslav Butusov, Leonid Porokhnyu, and local actors.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1492,"vote_count":11,"poster_path":"/45TCBRrgeGLJvFlpzUjTM9vPpEP.jpg","release_date":"1989-06-05","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Настя и Егор","original_language":"ru"},{"id":1378,"adult":false,"title":"Shortbus","video":false,"overview":"In post-9/11 New York City, an eclectic group of citizens find their lives entangled, personally, romantically, and sexually, at Shortbus, an underground Brooklyn salon infamous for its blend of art, music, politics, and carnality.","genre_ids":[10749,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.9638,"vote_count":562,"poster_path":"/s8QBrWgpZpYrySSyTQ0xbFLPKrS.jpg","release_date":"2006-10-04","vote_average":6.253,"backdrop_path":"/a9VOWosINcLNJQb3hNZAqEShVTM.jpg","original_title":"Shortbus","original_language":"en"},{"id":712454,"adult":false,"title":"The Summit of the Gods","video":false,"overview":"A photojournalist's obsessive quest for the truth about the first expedition to Mt. Everest leads him to search for an esteemed climber who went missing.","genre_ids":[16,12,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8673,"vote_count":399,"poster_path":"/iowz7MwaTWMYlfLUE6GeM0m3Hze.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-22","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/5vtEKq41KFezEnwIHmFrekQKNDy.jpg","original_title":"Le Sommet des dieux","original_language":"fr"},{"id":42691,"adult":false,"title":"Oedipus Rex","video":false,"overview":"In pre-war Italy, a young couple have a baby boy. The father, however, is jealous of his son - and the scene moves to antiquity, where the baby is taken into the desert to be killed. He is rescued, given the name Oedipus, and brought up by the King and Queen of Corinth as their son. One day an oracle informs Oedipus that he is destined to kill his father and marry his mother. Horrified, he flees Corinth and his supposed parents - only to get into a fight and kill an older man on the road…","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.3093,"vote_count":360,"poster_path":"/7R3yPlLdiNhpGzasB8SDCT6Kwy.jpg","release_date":"1967-09-07","vote_average":6.75,"backdrop_path":"/gNSXF2AKz3mTNT9CSWma9gxnwBR.jpg","original_title":"Edipo re","original_language":"it"},{"id":452,"adult":false,"title":"The Idiots","video":false,"overview":"A group of people gather at a Copenhagen suburban home to break all the limitations and to bring out the 'inner idiot' in themselves.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.1376,"vote_count":637,"poster_path":"/dZUgHe2XH8egBFerMC6yLoqUqii.jpg","release_date":"1998-04-28","vote_average":6.458,"backdrop_path":"/3l28DnWMafB4dEXdYROxw3HFaKD.jpg","original_title":"Idioterne","original_language":"da"},{"id":4593,"adult":false,"title":"The Discreet Charm of the Bourgeoisie","video":false,"overview":"In Luis Buñuel’s deliciously satiric masterpiece, an upper-class sextet sits down to dinner but never eats, their attempts continually thwarted by a vaudevillian mixture of events both actual and imagined.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0256,"vote_count":887,"poster_path":"/zN4ILX2x64PvT2jIOAHXxCOi5WA.jpg","release_date":"1972-09-15","vote_average":7.461,"backdrop_path":"/z6NI6n5MvQZMZJbXKLiyFl1yDeA.jpg","original_title":"Le Charme discret de la bourgeoisie","original_language":"fr"},{"id":37169,"adult":false,"title":"The Human Centipede (First Sequence)","video":false,"overview":"During a stopover in Germany in the middle of a carefree road trip through Europe, two American girls find themselves alone at night when their car breaks down in the woods. Searching for help at a nearby villa, they are wooed into the clutches of a deranged retired surgeon, who has a very disturbed vision.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.5122,"vote_count":2335,"poster_path":"/gMtjxIkEi0hnTV5lPHbgeZ4ZpUZ.jpg","release_date":"2009-10-31","vote_average":5.186,"backdrop_path":"/wubUakLEAAnKeXmuTks5insTKQx.jpg","original_title":"The Human Centipede (First Sequence)","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":26,"adult":false,"title":"Walk on Water","video":false,"overview":"Eyal, an Israeli Mossad agent, is given the mission to track down and kill the very old Alfred Himmelman, an ex-Nazi officer, who might still be alive. Pretending to be a tourist guide, he befriends his grandson Axel, in Israel to visit his sister Pia. The two men set out on a tour of the country, during which Axel challenges Eyal's values.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.8741,"vote_count":91,"poster_path":"/mVWFN3RaBFLuJRtRLPebatX9qPq.jpg","release_date":"2004-02-05","vote_average":6.835,"backdrop_path":"/z5YFbE9VVHwDXbXbqZdoO6THqPs.jpg","original_title":"ללכת על המים","original_language":"he"},{"id":28,"adult":false,"title":"Apocalypse Now","video":false,"overview":"At the height of the Vietnam war, Captain Benjamin Willard is sent on a dangerous mission that, officially, \"does not exist, nor will it ever exist.\" His goal is to locate - and eliminate - a mysterious Green Beret Colonel named Walter Kurtz, who has been leading his personal army on illegal guerrilla missions into enemy territory.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"popularity":11.5037,"vote_count":8898,"poster_path":"/gQB8Y5RCMkv2zwzFHbUJX3kAhvA.jpg","release_date":"1979-05-19","vote_average":8.267,"backdrop_path":"/eN5G8vTWLnZxJ0LTd4g27oPObcZ.jpg","original_title":"Apocalypse Now","original_language":"en"},{"id":64,"adult":false,"title":"Talk to Her","video":false,"overview":"Two men share an odd friendship while they care for two women who are both in deep comas.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":1.2447,"vote_count":1408,"poster_path":"/fWDbQlOWOqjR5jZm98KjGyYmUOw.jpg","release_date":"2002-03-15","vote_average":7.58,"backdrop_path":"/9aCRXFWT1rd1nZDcEtWILKb2Sap.jpg","original_title":"Hable con ella","original_language":"es"},{"id":66,"adult":false,"title":"Absolute Power","video":false,"overview":"A master thief coincidentally is robbing a house where a murder—in which the President of the United States is involved—occurs in front of his eyes. He is forced to run, while holding evidence that could convict the President.","genre_ids":[80,18,28],"popularity":2.2658,"vote_count":1203,"poster_path":"/izvyt3cxlilhbYwybTOteDWqf99.jpg","release_date":"1997-02-14","vote_average":6.658,"backdrop_path":"/cLftTzGw40BlLw8IggKSWDjKOQo.jpg","original_title":"Absolute Power","original_language":"en"},{"id":854356,"adult":false,"title":"Disobedience","video":false,"overview":"A university student wants to avenge his sister from a businessman who abandoned her after leaving her pregnant. To do this, he decides to seduce the man’s sister to make him suffer the same fate.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2122,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/83yPN3iBey7Xcl5mD5d9yhq6YfV.jpg","release_date":"1958-12-14","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"親不孝通り","original_language":"ja"},{"id":854152,"adult":false,"title":"Inubu: The Dog Club","video":false,"overview":"Hanai Sota is 22-years-old and a university student in the veterinary department. Since he was little, he has always loved animals. His apartment is full of animals that needed help. One day, Hanai Sota saves a dog that was being used in experiments. To save more of the animals, he sets up the \"Inubu\" club. His friend Shibasaki Ryosuke, among other people, joins the group. Shibasaki Ryosuke also loves dogs and is a student in the same veterinary department as Hanai Sota. They work hard to protect the animals. 16 years later, a report comes out. The report is about Hanai Sota, who was arrested.","genre_ids":[18,10751],"popularity":0.4494,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/982Vb7oAw6CWacnKbDjzan7QKIU.jpg","release_date":"2021-07-22","vote_average":6.75,"backdrop_path":"/nvOrS60C5x3pL4aAY5hlT7S6jY7.jpg","original_title":"犬部！","original_language":"ja"},{"id":854153,"adult":false,"title":"Reptile House","video":false,"overview":"A man looking to buy a snake gets far more than he bargained for as he is drawn into a mysterious woman's home of exotic reptiles.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":0.2176,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"2020-02-02","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Reptile House","original_language":"en"},{"id":15,"adult":false,"title":"Citizen Kane","video":false,"overview":"Newspaper magnate Charles Foster Kane is taken from his mother as a boy and made the ward of a rich industrialist. As a result, every well-meaning, tyrannical or self-destructive move he makes for the rest of his life appears in some way to be a reaction to that deeply wounding event.","genre_ids":[9648,18],"popularity":5.4972,"vote_count":5938,"poster_path":"/sav0jxhqiH0bPr2vZFU0Kjt2nZL.jpg","release_date":"1941-04-17","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/9Y85oA1y6toL2OACXdaC6iTl7eQ.jpg","original_title":"Citizen Kane","original_language":"en"},{"id":19,"adult":false,"title":"Metropolis","video":false,"overview":"In a futuristic city sharply divided between the rich and the poor, the son of the city's mastermind meets a prophet who 